00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:12,181
COP 5: Suspect in sight.

368
00:22:15,480 --> 00:22:16,981
(WOMAN GASPING)

369
00:22:19,760 --> 00:22:21,261
COP 4: Go inside. I'm heading back.

